From: Marek Vasut <marex@denx.de>
Date: Wed, 22 Apr 2020 12:45:58 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] ARM: dts: stm32: Add missing ethernet PHY reset on AV96
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.7.6
